@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "BookingAvailability Page";
}
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Flight Availability</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Arquivo CSS externo -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="centerBookingHeaad">
        <div class="herov2">
            <div class="navbarcustom">
                <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")" class="airline-do-Simao">Airline</a>
                <div class="leftnavbarcustom">
                    <div class="navitem"><a href="@Url.Action("Regsister", "Home")"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i> Login & Registration</a></div>
                    <div class="navitem"><a href="@Url.Action("BookingAvailability", "Home")">Book</a></div>
                    <div class="navitem"><a href="@Url.Action("CheckIn", "Home")">Check-In</a></div>
                    <div class="navitem"><a href="#">Contact</a></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2>Your Selection</h2>
        <h4>Geneva to Lisbon</h4>
        <h6>Your flights</h6>
        <div class="flight-card">
            <div class="flight-header">
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-time">19:55</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">CDG - Terminal 1</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-duration">6h 45m BRU</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">Duration: 10h 35m</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-time">07:30 +1 day</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">LIS - Terminal 1</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flight-airline">
                    ✈ Operated by TAP Air Portugal, Brussels Airlines
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="price-box economy" onclick="selectClass(this, 'economy')">
                        <p>Economy</p>
                        <h4>€581.02</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="flight-card">
            <div class="flight-header">
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-time">20:55</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">GEN - Terminal 1</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-duration">6h 45m BRU</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">Duration: 10h 35m</div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flight-time">08:30 +1 day</div>
                    <div class="text-muted">LIS - Terminal 1</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flight-airline">
                    ✈ Operated by TAP Air Portugal, Brussels Airlines
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="price-box economy" onclick="selectClass(this, 'economy')">
                        <p>Economy</p>
                        <h4>€223.99</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container text-end mt-4">
        <h3>Total price:EUR 805.01</h3>
        <p>Round trip price for all passengers (incl. taxes, fees and surcharges)</p>
        <button class="btn-primary-booking-search" onclick="confirmSelection()">Select</button>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <p>Fares are not guaranteed until you confirm your purchase by clicking the “Yes, book and pay for ticket” button.**</p>
        <p>The fare is only valid if all the flights are fully flown in the booked sequence. Otherwise the fare will be recalculated based on the actual flight routing.</p>
        <p>In case this flight is operated by an airline other than Lufthansa, baggage allowance, priority check in, seating terms, Fastlane option may differ.</p>
        <p class="mb-5">
            <!-- Adiciona espaçamento -->
            Please note that options (e.g.: extra baggage, seat reservation) are not refundable in case you cancel your flight or if you change your flight and the option is no longer available.
        </p>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer text-center">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Airline. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <style>
        .navbarcustombooking {
            display: flex;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); /* Cor com opacidade */
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: rgb(130, 89, 46);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1250px;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 1%
        }

        .centerBookingHeaad {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 20vh;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary-booking-search {
            background-color: rgb(130, 89, 46);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .airline-do-Simao {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgb(130, 89, 46);
            align-content: center;
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
